<div id="node-24447" class="node node-content-manuscript-metadata node-promoted node-sticky node-teaser clearfix" about="/?q=node/24447" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document">

        <h2>
      <a href="/?q=node/24447">A. Taylor papers</a>
    </h2>
    <span property="dc:title" content="A. Taylor papers" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-field-ms-title field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Title:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">A. Taylor papers</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-records field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Date:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">1895, 1945</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-extent field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Extent:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">1 file (2 items)</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-physical-description field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Physical description:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">manuscripts</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-historical-note field-type-text-long field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Historical note:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Mrs A. Taylor was an early Durban resident.  She was a pupil at the Girls' Model School in Albert Street around 1895.  This collection consists of her reminiscences of life in Durban a few years before the turn of the century.  Mrs Taylor originally sent her accounts to the <em>Natal Mercury</em>.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-digitised field-type-list-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS File list:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Available at KCAL</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-scope-and-content field-type-text-long field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Scope and Content:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The file contains two manuscripts: an account of school life in Durban when the author attended the Girls' Model School; and an account of domestic and social life in Durban.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-shelf field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Shelf:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">TAY</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-provenance field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Provenance:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Original collection, 1945</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ms-local-system-number field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">MS Local system number:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"> KCAL210586</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-6 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above clearfix"><h3 class="field-label">Manuscript Inventory: </h3><ul class="links"><li class="taxonomy-term-reference-0"><a href="/?q=taxonomy/term/500" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel" datatype="">Taylor, A /Papers</a></li></ul></div>  </div>

      <div class="link-wrapper">
      <ul class="links inline"><li class="node-readmore first last"><a href="/?q=node/24447" rel="tag" title="A. Taylor papers">Read more<span class="element-invisible"> about A. Taylor papers</span></a></li>
</ul>    </div>
  
  
