    <div id="block-block-11" class="block block-block">

    <h2>About Campbell Collection</h2>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p class="rtejustify">The Campbell Collections of the University of KwaZulu-Natal holds major resources for research into the history and culture of southern Africa and KwaZulu-Natal. The Collections comprise of an <a href="/?q=node/42">Africana Library</a>, a <a href="/?q=node/49">Furniture and Picture Collection</a> and a <a href="/?q=node/53">Museum of Ethnology</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>
          <div class="region region-footer-secondcolumn">
    <div id="block-block-13" class="block block-block">

    <h2>Address</h2>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Campbell Collections<br />
220 Gladys Mazibuko Road,<br />
(formerly Marriott Road),<br />
Durban 4001<br />
General Enquiries: (031) 260 1720<br />
Library: (031) 260 1710 / (031) 260 1716<br />
Email: <a href="mailto:campbellcollections@ukzn.ac.za">campbellcollections@ukzn.ac.za</a><br />
<a href="http://www.ukzn.ac.za">University of KwaZulu-Natal</a></p>
